Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.31,0:00:00.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.05,0:22:16.18,ED_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,ひとりきりのさびしさ　ひとときのほほえみ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.81,0:22:24.11,ED_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,あなたがくれるものは　みんないとしい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.86,0:22:33.79,ED_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,すぐそばにいても　触れられないもの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.33,0:22:42.71,ED_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,心は月のように　形をかえていくの？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.21,0:22:51.26,ED_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,かなわない約束も　かわかない涙も
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.01,0:23:02.19,ED_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,あなたがくれたものは　だきしめておどる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.31,0:00:00.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.05,0:22:16.18,ED_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,一個人的孤獨 一時間的微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.81,0:22:24.11,ED_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你為我帶來的瑰寶 一樣樣都令人愛不釋手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.86,0:22:33.79,ED_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,哪怕兩人之間的距離觸手可及 可無形之壁註定你我天人永隔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.33,0:22:42.71,ED_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我的心宛如明月 陰晴圓缺不斷變幻
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.21,0:22:51.26,ED_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,約定依舊無法實現 眼淚仍然不願乾涸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.01,0:23:02.19,ED_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,只能把你給的瑰寶 緊擁懷中驀然舞起..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.31,0:00:00.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.11,0:00:10.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,憎恨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.15,0:00:11.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.49,0:00:13.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孤獨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.78,0:00:14.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.33,0:00:19.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難過
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.54,0:00:20.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嫉妒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.20,0:00:22.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.92,0:00:26.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛苦..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.00,0:00:28.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,霧江同學
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.34,0:00:35.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 最近都不來部室 還以為妳退部了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.26,0:00:38.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是新谷同學請假之後第一次來這裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.68,0:00:40.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小..小此木
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.48,0:00:48.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又..消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.31,0:00:00.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.99,0:02:26.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪之九 怨念少女
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.29,0:02:32.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貞一
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.63,0:02:38.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好 夕子學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.59,0:02:40.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點 太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.72,0:02:41.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用跑的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.14,0:02:43.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？遵命遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.35,0:02:45.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好 貞一
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.31,0:02:47.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎..怎麼啦啊 夕子學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.35,0:02:50.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼呀 就是要緊緊抱著你而已呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.52,0:02:52.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高興嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.73,0:02:55.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？這..這個嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.90,0:02:58.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為你喜歡我對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.95,0:03:05.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因為..我喜歡夕子學姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.16,0:03:10.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是說 那個是騙人的？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.54,0:03:11.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不..不是騙人的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.71,0:03:14.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就再說一次給我聽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.46,0:03:16.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.67,0:03:18.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再一次對我說你喜歡我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.68,0:03:21.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說不出來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.93,0:03:23.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不..這個嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.47,0:03:25.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不願說嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.60,0:03:26.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒那回事..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.68,0:03:28.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就說呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.02,0:03:33.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快~一~點~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.77,0:03:34.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是..是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.36,0:03:36.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜歡妳..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.53,0:03:38.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽不見
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.78,0:03:39.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再大聲一點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.65,0:03:41.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜歡妳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.61,0:03:42.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再來！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.66,0:03:43.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜歡妳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.53,0:03:44.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還差一口氣！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.20,0:03:49.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我對夕子學姐..！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.04,0:03:50.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,霧江同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.16,0:03:52.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們在玩什麼相聲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.96,0:03:54.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼相聲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.50,0:03:56.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在正是要緊的時候 妳不要來亂啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.59,0:03:59.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夕子才是 一大早就擋著校門
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.59,0:04:00.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳才是來亂的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.42,0:04:03.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們還真是不覺得厭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.51,0:04:04.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三百六十五天都在那卿卿我我的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.22,0:04:07.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先不扯這些 新谷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.64,0:04:08.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關於昨天的事..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.73,0:04:15.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夕子學姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.23,0:04:17.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們走 貞一
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.19,0:04:19.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下啊 夕子學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.24,0:04:24.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夕子..生氣了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.58,0:04:30.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貞一
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.46,0:04:34.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說貞一啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.54,0:04:38.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 你這樣一聲不應很無聊啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.50,0:04:41.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在正在考試
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.59,0:04:43.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼關係嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.26,0:04:45.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在是考試中哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.84,0:04:47.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關係大著了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.55,0:04:49.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起這個 繼續剛才那個話題
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.39,0:04:50.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說你喜歡我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.81,0:04:53.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.56,0:04:54.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.85,0:04:55.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你不說給我聽的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.65,0:04:57.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就把試卷的答案說出來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.94,0:04:59.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以跑去看正確答案的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.27,0:05:01.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.78,0:05:03.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.99,0:05:05.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜歡妳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.49,0:05:07.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.45,0:05:09.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs60}喜歡妳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.62,0:05:11.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？只有這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.54,0:05:13.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs70}最喜歡妳了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.25,0:05:16.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 用嘴巴說出聲來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.29,0:05:18.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之後我們再慢慢說吧 貞一
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.21,0:05:21.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想這樣蒙混過關對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.46,0:05:22.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這可不行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.59,0:05:23.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛痛痛..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.63,0:05:24.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請住手啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.59,0:05:27.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.13,0:05:30.35,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}測驗時間 40分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.18,0:05:30.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,後面的人 把答案紙收起來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.77,0:05:33.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 等..等一下！
